            "description": "Create a new appraisal with multi-source quotes\n\nRequired:\n- dealershipId: Your assigned dealership\n- year, make, model\n- mileage: Vehicle mileage\n- condition: 1-5 (1=Poor, 5=Excellent)\n\nOptional:\n- vin: Vehicle VIN\n- trim: Vehicle trim level\n- options: Additional features\n- zip: Zip code for regional data\n\nReturns:\n- Appraisal ID\n- Quotes from multiple sources\n- Summary with low/high/average values"
          },
          "response": []
        }
